           multiply  w-buf-rig-rcc-pun    by   w-buf-rig-rcc-qta
                                        giving w-buf-rig-rcc-ibl      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Iva                                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Conversione                             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "CV"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      05                   to   v-car                  .
           move      rf-asz-ali-iva       to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-num                to   w-buf-rig-rcc-iva      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Imponibile se non calcolato                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test su imponibile calcolato            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-buf-rig-rcc-ibl    not  = zero
                     go to prn-liv-det-rcc-100.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Conversione                             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "CV"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      12                   to   v-car                  .
           move      rf-asz-ibl-rig       to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-num                to   w-buf-rig-rcc-ibq      .
______*    divide    100                  into w-buf-rig-rcc-ibq      .
       prn-liv-det-rcc-100.
