                     go to prn-liv-det-rcc-120.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Messaggio di errore                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-msg-liv-det-msg      .
           string    "Riga nr. "
                                delimited by   size
                     w-msg-liv-det-ctr
                                delimited by   spaces
                     " : ERRORE - Codice fornitore fuori sequenza !"
                                delimited by   size
                                          into w-msg-liv-det-msg      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Uscita per errore                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-liv-det-rcc-900.
       prn-liv-det-rcc-120.
